thread.title_full: TAXIBOX mobile self-storage reviewed by Danielle

author: Danielle
title: Danielle
text: Just what we needed at super competitive pricing. Conveniently delivered and collected from your home. Good communication about how to best use the boxes. Only lost star due to not being able to get our 1st choice of delivery dates due to them being so busy.
